Class StreamResponse

java.lang.Object
  org.firewaterframework.rest.Response
      org.firewaterframework.rest.StreamResponse

public class StreamResponse
extends Response

This class wraps an unstructured byte stream to hold the response payload. It is typically used for text or binary response payloads.
